## Limitations

The report is limited by the availability of recent and comprehensive data on car theft motivations. Some sources may have biases, particularly those from forums or opinion-based articles. Additionally, the rapidly changing nature of crime trends means that findings may quickly become outdated. Further research and updated statistics would be beneficial for a more thorough understanding.